<heading id="h-0003" level="1">BRIEF DESCRIPTION OF THE DRAWINGS</heading>
<p id="p-0011" num="0010">In the drawings:</p>
<p id="p-0012" num="0011"><figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. 1</figref> is a plan view of the cord component operatively disposed on a cleat;</p>
<p id="p-0013" num="0012"><figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. 2</figref> is a view similar to <figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. 1</figref> with the cord component tensioned during removal from a cleat.</p>
<p id="p-0014" num="0013"><figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. 3</figref> is a sectional view taken along line <b>3</b>-<b>3</b> of <figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. 1</figref>;</p>
<p id="p-0015" num="0014"><figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. 4</figref> is a sectional view taken along line <b>4</b>-<b>4</b> of <figref idref="DRAWINGS">FIG. 2</figref>; and</p>
